WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:04.520
So, some of the lifestyle changes that you can expect: number one, get

00:00:04.520 --> 00:00:08.180
 used to wearing uniform. You're going to be putting this thing on every

00:00:08.180 --> 00:00:11.850
 single day. We have a couple of different styles to choose from.

00:00:11.850 --> 00:00:15.520
 We can put on coveralls if we're on the ship. These are the cammies

00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:19.180
 that we wear when you're walking around a normal city but we also

00:00:19.180 --> 00:00:22.850
 have like, a dress whites and dress blues. They look really nice. Another

00:00:22.850 --> 00:00:26.520
 lifestyle change you can expect is to be following orders. So,

00:00:26.520 --> 00:00:30.180
 if you're working at McDonald's and you have a boss telling you, you

00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:33.850
 know, "Go to drive thru", "Go to make some breakfast in the morning",

00:00:33.850 --> 00:00:37.520
 so same thing, that's not going to change just because you're the

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:41.180
 military. In fact, it's going to get a little bit more intense you

00:00:41.180 --> 00:00:44.850
 could say. So, you're going to have, you know, five or six bosses.

00:00:44.850 --> 00:00:48.520
 They have a hierarchy and you're going to hear from one less than the

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:52.180
 other but you're going to be hearing, you know, what to do every single

00:00:52.180 --> 00:00:55.850
 day.

